.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201811%2F28%2FP2018112800413.htm&d=uyenQRwN%2F2p2tRNf%2Bb8L0WWYsxP5Z0Wle18NOkmjjC4%3D&h=cf9950f9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201811/28/P2018112800413.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n咁即係佢地而家<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">代表緊解放軍出動</span></span>, 要<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">推俾美國睇</span></span>!!!!!!!!!"},{"pid":"927df01d8018bacec13dc576abb300b224549cdc","tid":1765503,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T03:56:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"add85b076955bdac2c753fc0b5c065ae4c07e187","tid":1765503,"uid":280058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T03:57:45.000Z","msg":"出黎摺被呀屌"},{"pid":"a66e1303b5292553bd3d96ba823976103031abd9","tid":1765503,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T03:57:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ee4a40adeca7fa650f06977299ddb8dd2d54516","tid":1765503,"uid":107405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0555df7c2c0402595c8db9ef6cb4f29159444976","tid":1765503,"uid":169665,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T02:56:30.000Z","msg":"軍隊係對外, 唔係對內 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T03:58:02.000Z","msg":"中共軍隊只會對內 唔識對外<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"631f82de9c24aa24825f99050a84d1645b3a726f","tid":1765503,"uid":55747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T04:05:04.000Z","msg":"日日出黎買奶粉咖啦"},{"pid":"4b752578e1468c1ac330156de9be07a7bd9b60cd","tid":1765503,"uid":291656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T04:06:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"56fb38ce95bca71ed2c1c7b7e01091c3b4756da6","tid":1765503,"uid":128417,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T04:07:04.000Z","msg":"所以話同中國講合約精神真係on99<br />\n有晒白紙黑字都要合理化返自己做錯嘅事"},{"pid":"3363bf19760ac52a5654d4fb276f154cc587654b","tid":1765503,"uid":339472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5838bd9b8b42792afeecbcd2df471d243f861cb3","tid":1765503,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T02:19:02.000Z","msg":"【明報專訊】解放軍駐港部隊於半個月前，離開並步出軍營清理位於九龍塘一帶的路障，被質疑涉違反《駐軍法》。中聯辦前法律部長、清華大學國家治理研究院長王振民撰文支持做法，稱<span style=\"color: red;\">「如果駐軍一直封閉在軍營裏邊，就無法履行好守護香港的憲制責任」</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>「留在軍營難護港」</strong><br />\n王振民在《紫荊》雜誌撰文稱，一旦有緊急軍務、道路不通，勢必嚴重影響駐軍按《基本法》及《駐軍法》履行職責，清除路障，「是包括駐軍在內香港全社會共同的職責」；並稱駐軍若要履行好拱衛香港的法定職責，<span style=\"color: red;\">「也必須經常以適當的方式走出軍營，了解香港的社情民意和山山水水」</span>。文中又稱，駐軍多年以來進行大量公益活動，相信將來會一如既往，在履行防務職責外從事更多公益活動；對於港人質疑違反《基本法》、《駐軍法》，王振民稱<span style=\"color: red;\">「全世界的法律沒有禁止任何人做好事的」</span>。<br />\n<br />\n公民黨黨魁楊岳橋預料，王振民的說法是有意找理由，為駐軍的行動提供說法基礎，但他指出《基本法》14、18條均牽涉駐軍，質疑文中說法如何符合上述條文，<span style=\"color: red;\">「北京官員常說依法，不如告訴全港、全世界，聲稱自願清除路障是符合哪條（條文）？如找不到，憑何談依法？」</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E/article/20191202/s00001/1575224397442/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E8%25A6%2581%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20191202%2Fs00001%2F1575224397442%2F&d=uyenQRwN%2F2p2tRNf%2Bb8L0WWYsxP5Z0Wle18NOkmjjC4%3D&h=0ae712ba\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E8%25A6%2581%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20191202%2Fs00001%2F1575224397442%2F&h=ffe460ed\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E/article/20191202/s00001/1575224397442/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T04:07:20.000Z","msg":"去狗宿幫狗摺被"},{"pid":"3d3fba8e03e46a297073c5c6689571e79778de37","tid":1765503,"uid":301949,"like":2,"dislike":0,"sco